ISLAMABAD, Aug 04 (APP): Prime Minister Muhammad Shehbaz Sharif on Wednesday appreciated Pakistani weightlifter Nooh Dastagir Butt for winning a gold medal  for Pakistan in the Commonwealth Games with a record lift of 405kg.
On his Twitter handle, the prime minister posted ” Well done, Butt saab,” and also tagged a tweet with pictures of Pakistani weightlifter.
